article.headline: Sam Alajiki scores 16 to lead Oral Roberts to 105-49 victory over Ozark Christian
article.description: — Sam Alajiki scored 16 points as Oral Roberts beat Ozark Christian 105-49 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Sam Alajiki scores 16 to lead Oral Roberts to 105-49 victory over Ozark Christian
article.story: TULSA, Okla. -- — Sam Alajiki scored 16 points as Oral Roberts beat Ozark Christian 105-49 on Friday night. Alajiki added eight rebounds and three steals for the Golden Eagles (1-1). Darius Robinson Jr. scored 13 points with three steals. Jalen Miller shot 4 of 7 from the field and 4 for 6 from the line to finish with 13 points, while adding six assists. Micah Colburn led the way for the Ambassadors with 12 points and two steals. Curtis Davenport scored nine. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
